## 1Ô∏è‚É£ Functionality
- [ ] **Authentication**
  - [ ] Login, registration, and password reset work.
  - [ ] Google Sign-In works (if implemented).
  - [ ] Invalid credentials produce correct error messages.
- [ ] **Deposit Accounts**
  - [ ] Create account with chosen currency.
  - [ ] Join account via invite link (admin approval required).
  - [ ] Admin approval/rejection updates UI in real time.
- [ ] **Deposits**
  - [ ] Upload proof of deposit works.
  - [ ] Amount conversion to Kwacha and other currencies works.
  - [ ] Admin approval/rejection works and triggers notifications.
- [ ] **Withdrawals**
  - [ ] Request submission works.
  - [ ] Special condition approval logic works.
- [ ] **Profile**
  - [ ] Update username works.
  - [ ] Change password works.
  - [ ] Default currency setting works.
- [ ] **Theme Toggle**
  - [ ] Switches between light and dark mode.
  - [ ] Theme preference persists after restart.
- [ ] **Notifications**
  - [ ] Local notifications work.
  - [ ] Push notifications (FCM) work.

---

## 2Ô∏è‚É£ UI/UX
- [ ] AppBar design consistent across all screens.
- [ ] Text, buttons, and icons are readable and aligned.
- [ ] Consistent spacing and padding throughout the app.
- [ ] All images and icons load correctly.
- [ ] Currency values display with correct symbols and formatting.
- [ ] Works correctly in both portrait and landscape modes.
- [ ] Responsive layout across small, medium, and large screen sizes.

---

## 3Ô∏è‚É£ Performance
- [ ] App launches in under 3 seconds on mid-range Android devices.
- [ ] Smooth scrolling in all list views.
- [ ] No visible UI lag during navigation.
- [ ] Memory usage stable during heavy use.
- [ ] Offline mode handles gracefully with appropriate messages.

---

## 4Ô∏è‚É£ Security
- [ ] Firebase security rules enforce admin/member roles.
- [ ] Only account admins can approve/reject join requests, deposits, and withdrawals.
- [ ] No sensitive data stored in plain text locally.
- [ ] Invite links expire and cannot be reused after joining.
- [ ] All network requests use HTTPS.

---

## 5Ô∏è‚É£ Pre-Release Build
- [ ] Remove all console logs and debug print statements.
- [ ] Remove unused assets and dependencies.
- [ ] Run `flutter build apk --release` without errors.
- [ ] Install release APK on at least 2 different Android devices for final verification.

